Export Reports
JSON: app_scan_report.json

CSV: app_scan_report.csv

Notes
Detection is name-based: Apps are flagged if their names match entries in the threat database.

Database updates: Keep the JSON file current to improve detection accuracy.

Hash verification: Can be extended to compare against known malware signature lists.

Cross-platform limitations: Registry scanning works only on Windows; Linux/macOS rely on package managers.
